mysubs version 1.14.
===================

mysubs is a lexically-scoped pragma that implements lexical subroutines i.e. subroutines whose use
is restricted to the lexical scope in which they are imported or declared.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  B::Hooks::EndOfScope
  B::Hooks::OP::Annotation
  B::Hooks::OP::Check
  Devel::Pragma
  ExtUtils::Depends

